sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant UI as WebApp
    participant API as Settings API
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open company settings
    activate UI
    UI->>API: GET /company/settings
    activate API
    API->>DB: Query current settings
    activate DB
    DB-->>API: Settings data
    deactivate DB
    API-->>UI: 200 OK + settings
    deactivate API
    UI-->>User: Display settings form
    deactivate UI

    User->>UI: Update settings and submit
    activate UI
    UI->>API: PUT /company/settings (updated data)
    activate API
    API->>DB: Validate & persist settings
    activate DB
    DB-->>API: Save success
    deactivate DB
    API-->>UI: 200 OK
    deactivate API
    UI-->>User: Show success confirmation
    deactivate UI